claim.claim-text:
1. A method for presenting information, comprising: 
collecting at a client information about a user; 
transmitting via a network the collected information from the client to a location for generating a user profile for the user based on the collected information, wherein content is selected for the user based on the generated user profile; 
receiving the content at the client via the network; and 
presenting the content to the user at the client.

